import React from 'react'
import {
    SidebarContainer,
    Icon,
    CloseIcon,
    SidebarWrapper,
    SidebarMenu,
    SidebarLink,
    SideBtnWrap,
    SidebarRoute,
} from './SidebarElement'
const Sidebar = () => {
    return (
        <SidebarContainer>
            <Icon>
                <CloseIcon/>
            </Icon>
            <SidebarWrapper>
                <SidebarMenu>
                    <SidebarLink to="community">
                    커뮤니티
                    </SidebarLink>
                    <SidebarLink to="intro">
                    시설소개
                    </SidebarLink>
                    <SidebarLink to="reservation">
                    시설예약
                    </SidebarLink>
                    <SidebarLink to="map">
                    오시는길
                    </SidebarLink>
                </SidebarMenu>
                <SideBtnWrap>
                    <SidebarRoute to="/login">로그인</SidebarRoute>
                </SideBtnWrap>
            </SidebarWrapper>
        </SidebarContainer>
    )
}

export default Sidebar
